    "Unknown": "This is opposed to those secret and lesser sins, which are only known to and punished by God.\nVer.\n24. My hope, i.e. the matter of my hope and trust, placing my chief joy and satisfaction in worldly wealth, expecting safety and [v_Psa_62_10] happiness from it. Compare #Ps 62:",
