    "Commentary Vol. 91": "In the course of Providence this plotting and arresting had all taken place, that the Scriptures might be fulfilled; though the human actors had no such design. The Scriptures of the prophets, because the reference is especially to the predictive portions of [v_Jhn_19_28] Scripture, the Messianic prophecies; compare at the crucifixion,John `[char_John_Ref]` 19:"
